modShortDescription: A mod that allows you to increase steel strength to 50,000. Blocks, doors, spikes, stairs and much more. For A18 and A19.
modDescription:
A mod that allows you to increase steel strength to 50,000\. Blocks, [doors](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-doors/), spikes, stairs and much more. You just have to put this mod in the mod folder on the server and you’re done. For A18 and A19.

The mod can be used freely. Not sold or edited. The license lies with the sixth attempt and Herrath.

**[Download](https://www.dropbox.com/s/g1bsbx8lqlf0y8r/MaxDamage.rar?dl=1)**

If you appreciate Sechsterversuch’s work and you want to show support, use this [donate link](https://www.paypal.me/7daysserver584).
